{"377130":{"detail":{"date":"2026-04-06","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/27/ff/377130_wDU1x.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/27/ff/377130_wDU1x.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/27/ff/377130_wDU1x.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/27/ff/377130_wDU1x.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/27/ff/377130_wDU1x.jpg"},"summary":"众人皆以为魔法是与生俱来的血统，可可却意外撞见了通往魔女之路的另一种可能，这也让她陷入左右世界命运的争斗核心。\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[简介原文]\r\n生まれた時から魔法を使えない人は魔法使いになれないし、魔法をかける瞬間を見てはならないのがこの世界の掟。\r\nそれでも小さな村の少女・ココは、昔から魔法使いへの憧れを抱き続けていた。\r\nある日、村を訪れた魔法使い・キーフリーが魔法を使うところを見てしまい、大きな秘密を知る。\r\nそれは、特別な道具で魔法陣を描けば、本当は誰にでも魔法が使えるという、魔法使いたちが隠した「絶対の秘密」だった――。","name":"とんがり帽子のアトリエ","name_cn":"尖帽子的魔法工房","tags":[{"name":"2026年4月","count":790,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":691,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":673,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":525,"total_cont":0},{"name":"BUGFILMS","count":499,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2026","count":352,"total_cont":0},{"name":"魔法","count":308,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":302,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":263,"total_cont":0},{"name":"渡边步","count":200,"total_cont":0},{"name":"白浜鴎","count":105,"total_cont":0},{"name":"渡辺歩","count":55,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":52,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2025","count":44,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2026年","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"异世界","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"濑古浩司","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"待上映","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"中村悠一","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小泉纪介","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"斋贺光希","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"山村响","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"本村玲奈","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"久野美咲","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"月城日花","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"花江夏树","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"未确定","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"4月","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"瀬古浩司","count":4,"total_co